---
title: Stovetop Pastitsio-Inspired Fusilli with Greek-Style 'Bechamel' Sauce
description: Inspired by the classic Greek layered pasta dish, pastitsio, this stovetop version takes a fraction of the time to put together! Our Turkish Spice Blend lends this dish warm notes to give it those Greek flavours we expect from traditional pastitsio!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fusillis-poeles-facon-pastitsio-4cfe1b27.jpg
